OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,FScotland's Finance Secretary has said
OL,8,Fthe country is being "punished" for
OL,9,Fhaving a larger public sector due to
OL,10,Fthe UK Government's increase to
OL,11,Fnational insurance contributions.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves angered the
OL,14,FScottish Government when the decision
OL,15,Fto increase the payments from
OL,16,Femployers was announced in her October
OL,17,FBudget.
