OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,FShona Robison has estimated the cost
OL,8,Fto Scotland's finances could be #700
OL,9,Fmillion as a result of its bigger
OL,10,Fpublic sector workforce.
OL,12,FThe Chancellor announced funding to
OL,13,Fprotect the public sector in England
OL,14,Ffrom the increase, with a population
OL,15,Fshare of the cash likely to be between
OL,16,F#290 million to #350 million.
