OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of an appearance at the
OL,8,FLocal Government, Housing and Planning
OL,9,FCommittee at Holyrood this week, Ms
OL,10,FRobison warned of the impact the
OL,11,Fincrease could have on councils if not
OL,12,Fmitigated.
OL,14,F"Scotland's public services face a
OL,15,Fbill of more than #700 million as a
OL,16,Fresult of the UK Government's increase
OL,17,Fin employer national insurance
OL,18,Fcontributions," she said.
