OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,F"There have been indications of likely
OL,8,Ffunding reported in the media, but
OL,9,Fthese fail to take account of the fact
OL,10,Fthat we have a larger public sector
OL,11,Fper person than other parts of the UK,
OL,12,Fleaving us some #300 million short.
OL,14,F"It feels like Scotland is now being
OL,15,Fpunished for having decided to employ
OL,16,Fmore people in the public sector and
OL,17,Fto invest in key public services.
