OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,F"We know local authorities are already
OL,8,Funder significant financial pressure.
OL,9,FThis will only continue to build
OL,10,Funless the UK Government reimburses us
OL,11,Fin full for their tax increase.
OL,13,F"Councils are in the process of
OL,14,Fsetting their budgets now, so the
OL,15,Fsooner we have clarity over this issue
OL,16,Fthe better ` this is needed urgently.
