OL,3,CScotland 'being punished for bigger
OL,4,Cpublic sector' due to NI rise, says
OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,F"The Scottish Government will continue
OL,8,Fto work closely with Cosla to press
OL,9,Fthe UK Government to provide the
OL,10,Ffunding needed to support public
OL,11,Fservices in Scotland."
OL,13,FA spokesman for the UK Government
OL,14,Fsaid: "The Budget delivered more money
OL,15,Fthan ever before for Scottish public
OL,16,Fservices and the Scottish Government
OL,17,Freceives over 20% more funding per
OL,18,Fperson than equivalent UK Government
OL,19,Fspending.
