OL,5,CRobison
OL,7,F"It is for the Scottish Government to
OL,8,Fallocate this across its own public
OL,9,Fsector and meet the priorities of
OL,10,Fpeople in Scotland.
OL,12,F"It will also receive additional
OL,13,FBarnett funding on top of this record
OL,14,F#47.7 billion settlement as part of
OL,15,Fsupport provided in relation to
OL,16,Fchanges to employer national
OL,17,Finsurance."
